data.description: Welcome to 1216 N 5th St. This historic home offers many updates including high efficiency HVAC, newer roof and newer floors throughout the entire house. The kitchen has modern cabinetry and stainless steel appliances, with a fully equipped Butler's pantry.  This home boasts 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Enjoy a beautiful view from the gazebo style deck.  Detached garage with upstairs 625 sq. ft studio area. Great for guests and work space. Make your appointment today!
